  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK638">
<l>aṟikoṉ ṟaṟiyā ṉeṉiṉu muṟuti </l>
<l>yuḻaiyiruntāṉ kūṟal kaṭaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although the king be utterly ignorant, it is the duty of the minister to give (him) sound advice.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
